OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FIt will be a dry day with long
OL,6,Fperiods of sunshine. Feeling quite
OL,7,Fpleasant in the sun although a bit
OL,8,Fcooler over Shetland with a light
OL,9,Fnorthwesterly breeze.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FA bright end to the day then
OL,12,Fa dry and chilly night with long clear
OL,13,Fspells. Cloud increasing later across
OL,14,FShetland.
OL,15,
OL,16,CFriday:FMostly cloudy and rather cold
OL,17,Fover Shetland with a few showers
OL,18,Farriving from the north. Mainly dry
OL,19,Fand bright over Orkney.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
