OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FMainly
OL,6,Fdry but rather cold and cloudy over
OL,7,Fthe weekend with the odd shower.
OL,8,FMilder on Monday with some patchy rain.
